    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)">Office of <persName role="author">SIMEON LEO</persName>,</p>
            <p rend="align(right)">Insurance, Note and Exchange Broker,</p>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>404 BROADWAY</placeName>.</p>
            <p>Government Securities Bought and Sold.</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)"><placeName>New York</placeName>, <date><add>?</add> 8th
                1864</date></p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Editor of the Occident</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">Dr Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">Enclosed<lb/> I beg to hand you a ticket of admission<lb/> to our
                Entertainment to come off on the<lb/>
                <date>17th</date> of this month, at Niblos Saloon.<lb/> The object of our Assctn. is
                to raise sufficient<lb/> means to erect an Asylum for the Aged<lb/> &amp; Infirm of
                the Jewish Persuasion,<lb/> It has been in existence for two years<lb/> &amp; we
                have at present quite a large<lb/>
                <sic>ballance</sic> in The hands of our Treasr.<lb/> If it is in your power we
                should<lb/> feel most grateful for a notice in<lb/> your valuable paper Hoping you
                are quite<lb/> well I remain Your Very Obt<add>?</add></p>
            <p rend="indent(4)"><persName role="author">Simeon N. Leo</persName>
                <add>Asst</add> Stage Manger</p>
        </body>
    </text>
